方、别个问题，便容易找到门","box":[[111,925],[651,926],[651,944],[111,943]]},{"text":"路了。","box":[[111,958],[161,958],[161,977],[111,977]]},{"text":"27","box":[[614,1001],[633,1001],[633,1017],[614,1017]]}],"dimensions":{"height":1120,"width":736}}